how to put online my application with GIT


from project folder into terminal do : 


1. git init     to initialize a new git repository

2. heroku create app_name   to create a heroku project on heroku server

3. heroku keys:add          ? something for encpripting

3.5 manage secret keys
  heroku config:set GITHUB_USERNAME=joesmith

4. do the git stuff : 
  git add .
  git commit
  
  git push heroku master

5.  heroku addons:add heroku-postgresql

6.  heroku run rake db:migrate


here I am!

if you have to manually create db

heroku addons:add heroku-postgresql
heroku pg:info
heroku pg:psql

heroku restart
heroku open